\id COL - consultant approved:ready for publication. Published with 2004 Aruamu NT. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus.
\h Kolosi
\toc3 KL
\toc2 Kolosi
\toc1 Ak…®nafarir Namba 2, Pol Tesalonikan Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Baghava an Osiri
\mt1 Ak…®nafarir Pol Kolosin Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Bagha Osirizim
\mt2 O
\mt1 Kolosi
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Kolosi, a nguibar ekiar mam, a Esian Provins…®n iti. Egha a Efesus…®n nguibar ekiam mong an borogh…®n iti. Pol uab…® Kolosin nguibam…®n sios gamiz…® an otozir puvat…®. Pol Efesus…®n ikiava gumaziba amadaz…®, me ghua provins…®n kam…®n nguibar mabar sios…®n ingangarim gamua, egha uaghan Kolosin ghu.
\ip Pol kamagh…®n oraki, gumazir maba Kolosibar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®ghas…®ghasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gavgavim men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dan…®ngasa, ak…®nafarir kam osirigha me bagha anemada. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, Krais biziba bar dar dapanim. Krais uab…®ra uam e iniam, eght…® tuavir igharaziba en akurvaghan kogham. Tuavir igharazir kaba e inigh Krais…®n saghuiam…®n mangam. Krais…®n, God bar bizibar ingariz…® da otifi. Egh Krais…®n ingangarim…®n God ua bar biziba iniasa. Krais en aven iti, ez…® e gumazamizir igiabar otivigha Krais…®n arazibara g…®n zui.
\ip Pol ak…®nafarir kam osirigha gumazir pumuning gan…®ngiz…®, aning a inigha Kolosin ghu. Gumazir faragha itim, Tikikus. Ez…® an g…®rara itim, Onesimus, gumazir kam Pol Filemon bagh osirizir ak…®nafarim…®n an gun m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribagha ami.
\c 1
\ms1 Krais a biziba bar dar dapanim, ez…® God…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim ko an arazir aghuiba bar a giz…®fa
\mr (Sapta 1:1--3:4)
\p 
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Rom 1:7; Efesus 1:1\x*K…® Pol, God uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua Krais Iesus…®n aposel…®n ikiasa na m…®sefe. Ez…® k…® ko en aveghbuam Timoti, ga ia bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. Ia God…®n gumazamizir Kolosin nguibar ekiam…®n itiba gan adarasi, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ikia a ko poroghav itir darasi. Ga, e uan Afeziam God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, a ian apangkuvigh ian navibar amut…® ia navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®.
\s1 Ga ia bagha n…®ghn…®gha God m…®nabav…®ra iti
\p 
\v 3-4 \x - \xo 1:3-4 \xt Mak 4:8; 16:15; Jon 15:16; Efesus 1:13-16; 3:2; Filipai 1:3; 2 Timoti 4:8; Filemon 1:5; Hibru 6:10; 1 Pita 1:4; 5:12\x*Ga ian arazir aghuim baragha kamagh…®n fo, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n ikiava God…®n gumazamiziba bar, me gifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiaba bar ga ia bagha God ko m…®g…®a, ia g…®n…®ghn…®gha God m…®nabav…®ra iti. A en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n Afeziam.
\v 5 E fo, guiz…®n akam, an Akar Aghuim, a faragha ia bagha ghuz…®ma ia kamagh…®n oraki, bizir aghuir God ia dan…®ngamiba da An Nguibam…®n iti, egh ia da bagh m…®zuam…®va da iniam. Egha ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bizir kam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n, ia guizbang…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n ikiava God…®n gumazamiziba bar, me gifonge.
\v 6 Ez…® nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar, me Akar Aghuir kam…®n akuraz…®, gumazamizir av…®riba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiava an g…®n zuima, Akar Aghuim…®n dagher aghuiba otiva ghuav…®ra iti. Ez…® ia uaghan, arazir kamra ian tong…®n oto. Dughiar ia faragha God…®n apangkuvim…®n eghaghanim baregha bar guizbang…®ra a g…®fozim, dughiar kam iza dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir kamra ian tong…®n otogha, ian ingarav…®ra iti.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Kolosi 4:12; Filemon 1:23\x*Epafras Akar Aghuir kam ian sure gami, ez…® ia a g…®fo. Epafras, a ingangarir gumazir bar aghuir ga bar ifongezim, a ga ko ingarir mav. A ga gis…®n ian akurvagha, bar derav…®ra Krais…®n ingangarim gami.
\v 8 Egha Epafras ga m…®g…®a ga geghari, God…®n Duam ia gamima ia God…®n gumazamiziba deraghav…®ra me gifonge.
\s1 Pol Kolosin gumazamiziba gavgavim me dan…®ngasa God ko m…®gei
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Rom 12:2; 1 Korin 1:5; Efesus 1:8-9; 1:15-17; 5:10; 5:17; Filipai 1:9\x*Bizir kam bagha, ga fom…®ra ian araziba baragha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, ga zurara ia bagha God ko m…®gei. Ga kamagh…®n an azangs…®si, God…®n Duam fofozir aghuiba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ia dan…®ngt…®, n…®ghn…®zir kaba bar ia giz…®vagham. Eght…® bizir kam…®n ia God…®n ifongiam bar a g…®fogham.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Jon 15:16; Efesus 2:10; 4:1; Filipai 1:27; 1 Tesalonika 4:1; Hibru 13:21\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia Ekiam…®n gumazamizibar m…®n ik…®va an arazibar amut…®ma, a ia amir araziba dagh ifuegham. Egh ia ingangarir aghuir igharagha garir av…®ribar amuam. Egh ia uaghan God g…®fogham, eght…® fofozir kam bar mang…®va ekevegham.
\v 11-12 \x - \xo 1:11-12 \xt Efesus 1:18-19; 3:16; 4:2\x*Ez…® ga kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei, an gavgavir ekiar aghuim…®n, God gavgaviba bar ia dan…®ngt…®, ia tuivigh gavgavigh os…®mt…®ziba ateram, egh aghumra ik…®va os…®mt…®ziba g…®vaghamin dughiam m…®zuam. Egh ia bar akuegh…®va, en Afeziam m…®nabagh. A ia gamiz…®ma ia arazir aghuibar g…®n zui, egh bizir aghuir a ia bagha m…®seveziba iniam. Ia God…®n gumazamiziba ko da iniam, kar God…®n Nguibam…®n angazangarim…®n aven itir darasi.
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 1:13-14 \xt Luk 22:53; Efesus 1:6-7; 2:2; 1 Tesalonika 2:12; 2 Pita 1:11\x*Faragha m…®tarmem…®n gavgavim e ikez…®ma e an apengan itima, God en akuragha e inigha uan Otarim…®n gavgavim…®n apengan e at…®z…® an en Atrivim iti, Otarir kam a bar a gifonge. God uan Otarim…®n ingangarim…®n e gamiz…® e f…®riagh…®re, egha tuavir kamra an en arazir kuraba g…®n amada.\f + \fr 1:13-14 \ft Akar kam, ‚Äúm…®tarmem…®n gavgavim,‚Äù an m…®ngarimra kara: Satan ko bizir an ativaz…® an apengan itiba, kar tintinim…®n duar kuraba, aseba, adariaba, ko arazir kuraba bar mogh…®ra.\f*
\s1 Pol Krais…®n araziba ko an ingangaribar gun m…®gei
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Jon 1:18; 2 Korin 4:4; Hibru 1:3\x*E God…®n ganighan kogham, ez…® Krais an m…®rara gari. Krais an Otarir ivariam, a God ingarizir bizir kaba bar dar dapanim.
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Jon 1:3; 1:10; Rom 8:38; 11:36; Hibru 1:2; 2:10; 1 Pita 3:22\x*Ez…® Krais…®n agharim…®n, God uan nguibam…®n itir biziba ko nguazim…®n itir biziba bar dar ingari. Kar bizir e gariba ko garir puvat…®ziba, da ensel…®n gavgaviba ko duar gavgaviba ko aseba ko adariaba, ko bizir gavgaviba itiba. God Krais ko, aning bizir kaba bar dagh amiz…®, da bar Krais baghav…®ra iti.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Jon 1:1-3; 8:58; 17:5; 1 Korin 8:6\x*Ez…® bizir kaba t…®ghar otivam, Krais fom…®ra iti. Egha a biziba bar dagh amima da derav…®ra uari isasuigha bar derav…®ra ingari.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Aposel 26:23; 1 Korin 15:20; 15:23; Efesus 1:10; 1:22-23; Akar Mogomem 1:5\x*Krais, a sios…®n dapanim, ez…® sios an inivaf…®zim. Egha a uab…® ik…®r…®m…®rir igiam…®n faragha zuir gumazim. Krais God…®n Otarir ivariam, egha a faragha ovevem…®n ua d…®kafi. God ghaze, Krais uab…® biziba bar dar dapanim…®n ikiam. Kamaghsua, a Krais gamiz…®, a ua d…®kafi,
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Jon 1:16; 3:34; Kolosi 2:9\x*God kamagh…®n ifonge, an ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim ko an araziba ko an gavgaviba Otarir kam giz…®vagham, kamagh…®n God uab…® Krais…®n aven iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Krais God…®n m…®rara gari.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Rom 5:1; 2 Korin 5:18; Efesus 1:7; 1:10; 2:13; 2:16; 1 Jon 2:2\x*Bizir God ingariziba, da an saghon ikegha apanir arazibar a gami. Ez…® God kamagh…®n ifonge, a bizir kaba bar dar amut…® da uam a ko navir vam…®ra ikiam. A ghaze, a Krais…®n ingangarim…®n arazir kam damuam. Kamagh…®n amiz…® a Krais ataghiz…®ma a ter ighuvim…®n areme. Ez…® an ghuzim irez…® tuavir kam…®n en apanir araziba da g…®fa. Egha bizir a ingariziba a bar ua da iniz…® da uam a ko iti, bizir an Nguibam…®n itiba ko nguazim…®n itiba uaghara.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Rom 5:10; Efesus 2:12; 4:18; Taitus 1:15-16\x*Iarara, ia fom…®ra arazir kuraba ko n…®ghn…®zir kurabagh amuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia God…®n saghon ikiava uan n…®ghn…®zibar aven an apanim gami.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Efesus 2:14-16; 5:27; 1 Tesalonika 4:7; Taitus 2:14\x*Ez…® God kamagh…®n ifonge, a ia inigh ua bagh izam. Eght…® ia an gumazamizibar m…®n ik…®va, an damazim…®n bar zuegh…®va, arazir kuratam ian ikian kogham. Kamaghsua dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n Otarim angam…®ra gumazir m…®karzim sara areme, ez…® tuavir kam…®n God uam e ko navir vam…®ra inis.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Mak 16:15; Efesus 3:17; 1 Timoti 3:16; Hibru 3:14\x*Ez…® d…®penir guarim d…®penim…®n suiraz…® mogh…®n, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n suiragh bar tuivigh gavgavigh ik…®. Ia Akar Aghuim baregha dughiar kam…®n fo ia bizir aghuiba iniam, egha ia dav zuava n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. Egh ia akong…®va n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim atagh…®raghan mark…®. K…® Pol, k…® Akar Aghuir kam…®n ingangarir gumazim, egha e gumazamizir nguazim…®n itiba bar me bagha anekuri.
\s1 Pol sios bagha ingangarim gami
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Rom 5:3; 2 Korin 1:5-6; Efesus 1:23; 3:13; Filipai 3:10; 2 Timoti 1:8\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® ian akurvaghasa m…®zazim ini. Krais sios…®n akurvaghasa inizir m…®zaziba, da g…®vazir puvat…®. K…® da g…®vasava ami. Ez…® k…® sios…®n akurvaghasa ifonge, a Krais…®n inivaf…®zimra. Bizir kam bagha k…® bar akonge.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Efesus 3:2; 3:7-8\x*God uab…®, ian akurvaghasa na m…®sevegha, ingangarir kam na gan…®ngi, ez…® k…® sios…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n oto. Ez…® k…® derav…®ra God…®n akam akurir ingangarim nan iti.
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Rom 16:25-26; 1 Korin 2:7; Efesus 3:3-5; 3:9-10; 2 Timoti 1:10\x*Dughiar fom…®ra itibar iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, akar kam bar modo, ez…® gumazamiziba bar a g…®fozir puvat…®. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n gumazamizibar damazibar an azenim gir…®.
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Rom 9:23; 2 Korin 2:14; Efesus 1:18; 3:8; 1 Timoti 1:1\x*Ez…® God…®n n…®ghn…®zim kamak…®n, a uab…® Akar Aghuir modozir kam e an gumazamiziba, an en aka, eght…® e fogham, akar modozir kam a guizbang…®ra bar dera, egh Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bar men akuragham. Akar modozir kam kamak…®n, Krais ian navir averiabar aven iti, ez…® ia fo, a ia inight…® ia a ko mang…®va God…®n Nguibam…®n ik…®va, egh ia an bizir aghuiba iniam, ez…® ia bizir kam bagha m…®zuai.
\v 28 \x - \xo 1:28 \xt Efesus 4:13; 5:27\x*Ez…® e Krais…®n Akar Aghuim bar vaghvagha gumazamizibav k…®ri. E kamagh…®n ifonge, me Krais ko porogh ik…®va fofozir aghuitam…®n oteveghan kogham, eght…® e me inigh God…®n damazim…®n mangam. Kamaghsua, e n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozir aghuim…®n g…®n ghua men sure gamua, egha akar gavgavim me gan…®di.
\v 29 \x - \xo 1:29 \xt Aposel 20:20; 20:27; Efesus 3:7; 3:20; Filipai 4:13\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Krais na gan…®ngizir gavgavir ekiam, a nan akurvazima, tuavir kam…®n k…® os…®mt…®ziba sara ingangarir dafar kam gami.
\c 2
\s1 E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®va akar ifavariba batogham
\p 
\v 1 K…® ia foghasa, k…® akurvazir ingangarir dafam ia ko Laodisian nguibam…®n itir gumazamiziba bagha a gami, egha uaghan nan guam…®n ganizir puvat…®zir igharaziba sara.
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Efesus 3:4; 3:18; Filipai 3:8; Kolosi 1:26; 3:14\x*K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, k…® gavgavim men navibar an…®ngt…® me atiatingan kogham, egh k…® me damut…® me uari gifuegh…®va uari inigh ik…®va, fofozir aghuim inight…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuir kam me damut…® men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bar ekevegham. Egh kamagh…®n me God…®n akar modozim…®n m…®ngarim deraghv…®ra a g…®fogham, a Krais, a uab…® akar modozir kam…®n m…®ngarim. Kamaghsua k…® ingangarir kam gami.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Aisaia 45:3; 1 Korin 1:24; 1:30; Efesus 1:8; 3:19\x*God…®n fofozir aghuim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuim bar p…®n kogha Krais giz…®vagha modogha iti, mati dag…®aba dag…®abar d…®penim…®n iti. Ez…® Krais uab…®ra fofozir aghuir kam en aka.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Rom 16:18; Efesus 4:14; 5:6; Kolosi 2:8\x*Ez…® k…® ghaze, tav ia gifar…®va akar am…®rizibar ia m…®k…®m…®va ia apezaperan kogham. Kamaghsua, k…® akar kam ia m…®gei.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt 1 Korin 5:3; 14:40; 1 Pita 5:9\x*K…® uab…® uan m…®karzim…®n ia ko itir puvat…®gha, k…® ia g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n k…® akurvazir ingangarir dafar kam ia bagha a gami. Egha k…® ian garima, ia uari inigha tuivigha deragha ingara egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n iti. Bizir kam bang…®n k…® bar akonge.
\s1 E Krais…®n porogh egh tuivigh gavgavigham
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® ia Krais Iesus en Ekiam a inigha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…® ia a ko daruva an porogh…®v ik…®.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Efesus 2:20-22; 3:17; Kolosi 1:23\x*Egh ia a gis…®n tuivigh gavgavigh, mati temem biba sara nguazim…®n tugha gavgafi. Uaghan mati d…®penim d…®penir ak…®nir gavgavibagh is…®n tughav iti. Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Akar Aghuir Epafras ian sure gamizir kam…®n iti, egh kamagh…®n ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim aghung mang…®v…®ra ik…®. Egh zurara God m…®nab…®v…®ra ik…®.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Galesia 4:3; 4:9; Efesus 5:6; Kolosi 2:3; 2:18-20; Hibru 13:9\x*Ia bar deragh uari bagh gan, gumazitam fofozir ifavariba ko akar k…®nitabar gun ia m…®k…®mt…®ma, ia an n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n mangan mark…®, eght…® da ia ik…®rarighan kogham. Gumazir kaba, inazir afeziaba ko duar kurar overiam ko nguazim gativaziba, me me da fofozir kaba ini. Ez…® fofozir kaba da Krais…®n izezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Jon 1:14-16; Kolosi 1:19\x*Ia fo, Krais a en m…®rara gumazim…®n oto, ez…® God…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim ko araziba ko an gavgaviba bar a giz…®fa.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Efesus 1:21-22\x*Egha a duar gavgaviba ko bizir gavgaviba itiba bar, dar dapanim. Ia Krais…®n poroghav itima, God ia gamima ia guizbang…®ra angam…®ra ikiav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Rom 2:29\x*Ez…® ia Krais…®n poroghav ikia, mati ia uan m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghorir arazim ini. Ez…® arazir kam, gumazitam uan dafarim…®n a gamiz…® an otozir pu. Puvat…®. Krais uab…® m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghorir arazir kam at…®. Krais…®n arazir kam…®n e, navir ghurim…®n gavgavir e ikiaghar…®gh…®zim, anetughavk…®nigha, a g…®n amadagha f…®riagh…®r…®. Kar guizbang…®ra m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir arazim.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Rom 6:4; Efesus 1:19-20; 3:7; Kolosi 3:1\x*Ez…® dughiar e ruezim…®n e Krais ko poroghav itima, God Krais ko e sara mozim gat…®. Ez…® e fo, God uan gavgavir ekiam…®n amodogh…®n ingarava Krais mozim…®n a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi. Ez…® e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ingangarir gavgavir kam…®n iti, ez…® dughiar e ruezim…®n, God Iesus ko e gamiz…®ma e uaghan ua d…®kafi.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Efesus 2:1-5\x*Ia faragha uan arazir kurabagh amir arazim bang…®n, ia mati gumazir m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir puvat…®zibar m…®n amua, gumazir aremezibar m…®n iti. Ia navir ghurim…®n arazibar g…®n zui. Dughiar kam…®n Krais ian navir ghurim…®n araziba t…®ghar da atughuvk…®nigh…®va da g…®n amadagham, kamagh…®n amiz…® ia gumazir aremezibar m…®n amuav…®ra iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n God ia gamiz…® ia Krais ko angam…®ra iti. Ez…® God en arazir kuraba bar a da g…®n amada.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Efesus 2:14-16; 1 Pita 2:24\x*Moses Osirizir Araziba, akam e gasaragha, en arazir kuraba aghurigha azenim gat…®gha, e gamima e an akam ko an gavgavim…®n apengan iti. Ez…® e gasir akar kaba God bar da batoke, egha uaghan Moses Osirizir Araziba isa Iesus…®n ter ighuvim…®n a gafu, egha tuavir kam…®n Moses Osirizir Arazibar gavgavim ag…®fa.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Kolosi 1:13\x*Ez…® Krais ter ighuvim…®n duar gavgaviba ko bizir gavgaviba itiba, a dar gavgaviba adegha g…®fa. God ter ighuvim…®n, kamagh…®n gumazamiziba bar men aka, a bar da d…®kab…®ragha dagh amima da pura bizir k…®nibar m…®n otifi.
\s1 E Krais koma areme, ez…® nguazir kam…®n araziba en akuraghan kogham
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Rom 14:1-12; 1 Korin 8:8; Galesia 4:10\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia tav ateght…®ma an akaba ia gasan mark…®, egh ia m…®k…®m suam, ia dagheba ko d…®paba apir arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®, o ia God…®n ziam fer dughiabar g…®n zuir puvat…®, o iak…®nir igiabar isar araziba ko Sabat…®n dughiabar arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Hibru 8:5; 9:9; 10:1\x*Arazir kaba, da bizir g…®n izamibar nedazir k…®niba, ez…® Krais a uab…® guizbang…®n bizim.
\v 18 Eght…® gumazitam bizitam irebam…®n m…®n bizim…®n ganigh, kamagh…®n a uab…®ra uan ziam f…®t…®, ia an akam baraghan mark…®. Gumazir kam suam, ia uarigh ifar…®va uari d…®kab…®n…®va egh enselbar ziaba f…®. Eght…® ia an akam baraghan mark…®. Gumazir kam a uan n…®ghn…®zim ko navir ghurim…®n arazibar g…®n ghua, pura m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® uab…® bar fo. Eght…® ia gumazir kamagh…®n amitam ateght…® a ia d…®kab…®ragh, ian ivezir aghuim ok…®man mark…®.
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Efesus 2:21; 4:15-16\x*Egha a Krais…®n suirazir puvat…®gha anetaki, Krais en dapanim, e an inivaf…®zim. E an poroghav ikia dagheba isa, egha a ko inivaf…®zir ag…®ribar m…®n uari isasuiragha iti. Inivaf…®zir kam Krais…®n apengan itima an a gamima a God ifongez…® mogh…®n aghua gavgafi.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Galesia 4:3-5; 4:9\x*Ez…® ia Krais ko poroghav ikia a ko areme, kamagh…®n amiz…® ia duar kurar overiam ko nguazim gativaziba bar ada ategha uam adar apengan itir puvat…®. Egha tizimsua ia nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizibar m…®n aruav…®ra iti? Egha tizimsua ia nguazir kam…®n arazibagh amuav…®ra iti? Arazir kaba kamak…®n,
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt 1 Timoti 4:3\x*‚ÄúIa bizir kabar suighan mark…®,‚Äù egh ‚ÄúDagher kabar aman mark…®,‚Äù egh uaghan ‚ÄúBizir igharazir maba sara suighan mark…®.‚Äù
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Aisaia 29:13; Matyu 15:9\x*Ez…® bizir kaba, e dar ingangaribagh amima da zuam…®ra ikufi. Arazir kaba, gumazamizibara uari dagh amuava da ar…®gha en sure gami.
\v 23 E bar fo, arazir kaba me dav k…®m suam, da n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar g…®n zui. Da guizbang…®ra bar puvat…®. Arazir kaba ghaze, ia uari uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…®va m…®gh…®ghv…®ra God…®n ziam fer arazibar amu. Egha ghaze, ia uarigh ifar…®va uari d…®kab…®n. Egha ghaze, ia God…®n ingangarim damuva uan m…®karzim m…®zazir kuram a dan…®ng. Egh arazir kaba, da en m…®karzibar akuragh navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®ragh da g…®vaghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.
\c 3
\s1 E Krais ko ua d…®kavigha ik…®r…®m…®rir igiam…®n iti
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Onger Akaba 110:1; Mak 12:36; 16:19; Efesus 1:20; Kolosi 2:12\x*God ia gamiz…®ma ia Krais ko ua d…®kavigha ik…®r…®m…®rir igiam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia God…®n Nguibam…®n p…®n itir biziba bar dagh ifongegh, da Krais iti nagh…®n iti. Krais, God…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan uan atrivir dabirabim…®n aperaghav iti.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Matyu 6:33\x*Ez…® ia bizir p…®n itiba baghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, egh nguazim…®n itir bizibagh n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Rom 6:2; 2 Korin 5:7; 5:14; Galesia 2:20; Kolosi 2:20\x*Ia fo, ia aremegha g…®fa, ez…® ian ik…®r…®m…®rir angam…®ra itim Krais ko ikiava, God…®n poroghav ikia egha modoghav ikia t…®ghar azenim…®n otivam.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Jon 11:25; 14:6; 1 Korin 15:43; Filipai 1:21; 1 Jon 3:2\x*Ez…® Kraisra, a guizbang…®ra ian ik…®r…®m…®rir angam…®ra itim…®n m…®ngarim. Eght…® Krais uamategh izamin dughiam, ia uaghan a ko an angazangarir gavgavir ekiam…®n aven otivam.
\ms1 Krais en aven itima // e gumazamizir igiabar otifi
\mr (Sapta 3:5--4:18)
\s1 Ik…®r…®m…®rir ghurim koma ik…®r…®m…®rir igiam
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Rom 6:6; 6:11-13; 8:13; Galesia 5:24; Efesus 4:19; 5:3-5; 1 Tesalonika 4:5\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia nguazim…®n itir arazir kurar ian navir averiam…®n itiba bar da g…®fagh. Bizir kaba, gumazamiziba uari bak…®a uari ko akuir arazim, ko arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba, ko afiar araziba, ko arazir kurabar amuasa naviba d…®kavir arazim, koma gumazir igharazibar bizibar gara da ifuer arazim. Bizibar gara dagh ifuer arazir kam, mati ia uari isa ifavarir godbar an…®ngizir arazim…®n m…®n ami.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Efesus 5:6\x*Ez…® bizir kaba bagha God uan an…®ngagharim…®n ivezir bar kuram gumazir arazir kabagh amiba me bagha anet…®z…®ma a iti. Kar gumazamizir God…®n akam iriagh…®riazibar ivezir kuram. A izam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Rom 6:19-20; 1 Korin 6:11; Efesus 2:2\x*Ia faragha arazir kurar kabar g…®n zuima, da ia gativagha ia ikiaghar…®ki.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Efesus 4:22; 4:25-31; 5:4; Hibru 12:1; 1 Pita 2:1\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia arazir kaba uam adar amuan mark…®. Arazir kaba: adariba, ko an…®ngaziba, ko navir kuraba ko akar kuraba uari gasir araziba, koma m…®g…®r…®g…®ar m…®z…®r…®zir ian akatoribar otiviba,
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Efesus 4:22\x*ko uarigh ifarir arazim, ia arazir kabar amuan mark…®. Ia fo, ia navir ghurim…®n araziba ategha,
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Jenesis 1:26; Rom 12:2; Efesus 2:10; 4:24\x*gumazamizir igiabar otifi, mati gumazim korotiar ghurim sueghava korotiar igiam aru. Ez…® God, gumazir ian ingariz…® ia gumazamizir igiabar otivizir kam, a kamagh…®n ifonge, a ia damut…® ia bar derav…®ram a g…®fogham. Kamaghsua, a ia gamuav…®ra itima ia an m…®raram otivav…®ra iti.
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Rom 10:12; Galesia 3:28; Efesus 1:23\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n b…®b…®ziba puvat…®. Ia ua kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, e Judaba ko Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, o e m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghore, o da aghorezir puvat…®, o igharazir darazir akabav gei, o nguibar atiabar gumazamiziba, o e pura ingangarir gumazibar iti, o e f…®riagh…®rezir gumazamiziba. E kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. E fo, Krais uab…®ra iti, egha Krais uab…® bar en aven iti.
\s1 E igharazibagh ifongezir arazim damuam
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Galesia 5:22; Efesus 4:32; Filipai 2:1; 1 Pita 2:9\x*\x - \xo 3:12-13 \xt Efesus 4:2\x*God ua baghav…®ra ia m…®sevez…®, ia an gumazamizibar otivigha g…®fa, ez…® a bar ia gifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia arazir kabar amu: Ia gumazamizibar apangkuv, egh arazir aghuibar gumazamizir igharazibar amu, egh uari d…®kab…®ragh, egh gumazamizibar asughasugh, egh d…®ghorim am…®razir arazim damu.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Mak 11:25; Efesus 4:32; 5:2\x*Egh ian tong…®n tav arazir kuratam igharazitav damight…®ma an an osemegh…®va, egh ia zuam…®ra uari uarir an…®ngaghan mark…®, egh uari uan arazir kuraba g…®n amang. Ia fo, Ekiam ian arazir kuraba g…®n amada, ez…® kamagh…®ra ia uaghan uarira uan arazir kuraba g…®n amang.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Rom 13:8-10; 1 Korin 13:13; Efesus 4:3\x*Egh ia bar uarigh ifongegh. Arazir kam a bar arazir igharazibagh afira. Arazir kam, an arazir aghuir igharazibagh amima da bar derav…®ram otiva, uari isa ingari.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Korin 12:13; 12:27; Efesus 2:16-17; 4:4; Filipai 4:7\x*Krais navir am…®rizim ia gan…®ngi, egha ia gamiz…®ma ia navir vam…®ra iti, ez…® navir am…®rizir kam ian navir averiabar ik…®va ia gativagh n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ia dan…®ngam. Ia fo, navir am…®rizir kam bagha God ian diaz…®ma ia bar uari inigha inivaf…®zir vam…®ran m…®n oto. Egh zurara God m…®nab…®.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Korin 14:26; Efesus 5:19; Kolosi 4:6\x*\x - \xo 3:16-17 \xt Efesus 5:19-20\x*Egh Krais…®n akam ian navir averiabar ik…® gavgafigh. Eght…® ia vaghvagh n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozibar g…®n mang…®va uarira uarir sure damuva akurvazir akam uari dan…®ng. Egh Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim…®n aven ighiabar amuva, Iesus…®n ziam fer ighiabar amuva, God…®n Duam ian navir averiabagh at…®zir ighiabar amu. Dughiar ia ighiabar amuamim, ia uan navir averiabar God m…®nab…®.
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Korin 10:31; Efesus 5:20; 1 Tesalonika 5:18; Hibru 13:15\x*Ez…® bizir manaba ia dagh ami, m…®g…®r…®g…®aba o ingangariba, ia bizir kaba bar Ekiam Iesus…®n ziam…®n dar amu. Egh an ziam…®n ia God Afeziam m…®nab…®.
\s1 Pol, Krais…®n arazibar g…®n mangasa, poroghamiba ko boribav gei
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Efesus 5:22; Taitus 2:5; 1 Pita 3:1\x*Ia amuiba vaghvagh, uan pabar apengan ik…® me bagh…®v…®ra ik…®. Kar Ekiam ifongezir arazim.
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Efesus 4:31; 5:25; 5:28; 1 Pita 3:7\x*Ez…® ia paba vaghvagh, uan amuiba bar deraghv…®ra me damuva bar me gifongegh. Egh men ataran kogh, paz…® me damuan mark…®.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Efesus 5:24; 6:1; Taitus 2:9\x*Ia boriba, ia zurara uan ameboghfeziabar akaba baragh…®va dar g…®n mang…®. Ia fo, Ekiam ian arazir kam bagh bar akuegham.
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt Efesus 6:4\x*Ia afeziaba uan boriba m…®gh…® me amir biziba bagh m…®k…®m…®va men n…®ghn…®zibar amut…® me ataran mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, borim osemegh kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, k…® bizitam damuan kogham. Mark…®. K…® aghua.
\s1 Pol ingangarir gumaziba ko gumazir ekiar men garibav gei
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt 1 Timoti 6:1; Taitus 2:9\x*\x - \xo 3:22-25 \xt Efesus 6:5-8\x*Ia ingangarir gumaziba vaghvagh, uan gumazir ekiar ian garibar akaba baragh, egh biziba bar dar amu. Egh ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, ‚Äúegh suam, dughiar me en gara itibar, e me apezeper ingangarir aghuibar amut…® me e gifuegham.‚Äù Puvat…®. Ia Ekiam…®n atiating, egh dughiaba bar uan navir averiabar aven derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, guizbang…®ra ingangarim damu.
\v 23 Ez…® ia amir biziba bar, ia uan gavgaviba sara dar amu. Kar, ia gumaziba bagha ingarir puvat…®. Ia Ekiam bagha ingangarim gami.
\v 24 \x - \xo 3:24 \xt 1 Korin 7:22\x*Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, ia Ekiam Krais…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba, a uab…®ra ian garir gumazir bar ekiam. Egha ia fo, Ekiam ivezir aghuir uan gumazamiziba bagha at…®zim, a g…®n ia dan…®ngam.
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt God…®n Araziba 10:17; Rom 2:11; Efesus 6:9; 1 Pita 1:17\x*Ia fo, God gumazamizir vabara a men garir puvat…®, a bar gumazamizibar gara men araziba ko navir averiaba derav…®ra dar gara tuavir vam…®ra me tuis…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir arazir kurabagh amizim, a uan arazir kurar an amizim bagh ivezir kuram iniam.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Ofa Gami 25:43; 25:53; Efesus 6:9\x*Ia ingangarir gumazamizibar garir gumazir ekiaba, ia kamagh…®n fogh, ia uaghan gumazir ian garir ekiam a God…®n Nguibam…®n p…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uan ingangarir gumazamiziba derav…®ra men gan…®va God…®n damazim…®n derazir arazim…®n me damuva arazir aghuibar me damu.
\s1 E God ko m…®geir arazim pamtem a damu egh deraghv…®ra daruam
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Efesus 6:18; Filipai 4:6\x*Ia God ko m…®k…®m mamagh…®ra ik…®va, deraghv…®ra gan…®va n…®ghn…®gh God ko m…®k…®m, egh God m…®nab…®v…®ra ik…®.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt Rom 15:30; 1 Korin 16:9; Efesus 6:19\x*Ia God ko m…®k…®m…®va egh uaghan e bagh an azangs…®ght…®, an e bagh tiam kuight…®ma e Krais…®n akam akunam. Akar kam a fom…®ra modoghav iti. Ia fo, k…® akar kam akuniz…®, me a baraghan aghuagha na isa kalabus gat…®.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Efesus 6:20\x*Ia God ko m…®k…®m egh suam, a nan akuraght…® k…® God ifongezir mogh…®ra, deraghv…®ra akar kam akunam.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Efesus 5:15-16; 1 Tesalonika 4:11-12\x*Ez…® ia, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n itir puvat…®zir darasi, ia n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar g…®n mang…®va egh arazir aghuibar me damu. Egh ia dughiaba vaghvagh Krais…®n arazibar men akakaghs…®v…®ra damuv…®ra ik…®.
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Mak 9:50; Efesus 4:29; Kolosi 3:16; 1 Pita 3:15\x*Ia zurara akar aghuir s…®ngt…®zibav k…®mt…®ma, gumazamiziba da baragh dagh ifuegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia bar derav…®ra fogh…®va gumazamiziba vaghvagh men akaba ikarvagh.
\s1 Pol Tikikus ko Onesimus aning amadaz…® aning Kolosin zui
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Aposel 20:4; 2 Timoti 4:12\x*\x - \xo 4:7-8 \xt Efesus 6:21-22\x*Tikikus e ko ingangarir gumazir mam, a en aveghbuar aghuir e bar ifongezim, egha a guizbang…®ra Ekiam…®n ingangarir gumazir bar aghuim. A nan ingangariba bar dar gun ia m…®k…®mam.
\v 8 Ez…® bizir kam bagha, k…® ia bagha anemada. K…® ghaze, ia fogham, e manmagh…®n iti, eght…® akar kam gavgavim ian navibar amut…® ia ua bar akuegham. Kamaghsua, k…® Tikikus amadaz…®, a ia bagha zui.
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt Filemon 1:10-12\x*Eght…® Onesimus, a Tikikus ko izam, a guizbang…®ra en guiz…®n aveghbuar bar aghuir e bar ifongezim, a dughiaba bar God…®n ingangarim gami. A ian mav. Eght…® aning bizir kagh otiviziba bar dar gun ia m…®k…®mam.\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Onesimus a pura Filemon…®n ingangarir gumazim. N…® akar Filemon ak…®nafarir Pol a bagha osirizim…®n aven itim…®n gan.\f*
\s1 Pol Kolosiba bagha ak…®nafarim amaga ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Aposel 12:12; 12:25; 13:13; 15:37-39; 19:29; 27:2; Filemon 1:24\x*Aristarkus, a na ko kalabus…®n ikia, egha ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. Ez…® Mak, Barnabas…®n imurim, a uaghan akam amaga ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. (Egh a iz…® ian tong…®n otoght…® ia a inigh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®. Ia Mak iniasa, k…® ia bagha akar kam amadagha g…®fa.)
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus, an ziar mam Jastus, a uaghan ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. Judan tong…®n itir gumazir m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorezir kabara, me na ko ikia God Gumazamizibagh Ativir Ingangarim gamua egha me bar deraghav…®ra nan akurvasi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Kolosi 1:7; Filemon 1:23\x*Epafras uaghan ia g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. A uaghan ian mav, egha Krais Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazim. A zurara ia bagha pamten God ko m…®g…®av…®ra iti, egha ghaze, God ian akurvaght…®, ia tuivigh gavgavigh, egh fofozir aghuitam oteveghan kogh…®va, egh God…®n ifongiam bar a g…®fogh…®va an g…®n mangam.
\v 13 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa, a bar akurvazir dafam ia bagha a gamuava egha uaghan Laodisian nguibam…®n itir darazi ko Hierapolis…®n nguibam…®n itir darazi bagha a gami.
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt 2 Timoti 4:10-11; Filemon 1:24\x*Ez…® Luk, a doktan e bar ifongezim, a Demas ko aning ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Gumazir av…®riba n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Luk…®n kamrama, ak…®nafarir pumuning osiri, mam Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim, egha igharazim Aposelbar Ingangariba.\f*
\p 
\v 15 Egh ia Laodisian itir sios…®n m…®k…®m suam, Pol ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. Egh ia Nimfa ko sios…®n an d…®penim…®n uari akuvim sara, bar me m…®k…®m suam, Pol ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®.
\v 16 Egh ia ak…®nafarir kam uarir tong…®n a d…®pon, egh g…®n Laodisian itir sios bagh anemadagh, eght…® me uaghan uarir tong…®n a d…®ponam. Egh uaghan ak…®nafarir k…® Laodisiaba bagha amadazim, me ia bagh anemadaght…®, ia a inigh…®va uarir tong…®n a d…®ponam.
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Filemon 1:2\x*Egh ia kamagh…®n Arkipus m…®kemegh, ‚ÄúEkiam n…® gan…®ngizir ingangarim, n…® derav…®ra a damuva bar aneg…®fagh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt 1 Korin 16:21; 2 Tesalonika 3:17\x*K…® Pol, k…® uan dafarimning…®n akar abuananam ia bagha an osira ghaze: God derav…®ra ia damu. K…® kalabus…®n ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® ia na g…®n amangan mark…®. K…® ia bagha God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, God…®n apangkuvim ia ko ik…®.\f + \fr 4:18 \ft N…® 1 Korin 16:21…®n gan.\f*
